    dcterms:isPartOf :section_4_1_1_introduction_and_highlight_rare_highly_capable_reckless_actions ;
    rdfs:comment "The alignment argument runs from higher capability to greater scope of harm, less intuitive tool use, and weaker casual oversight, which together raise release-time alignment risk."@en ;
    :canonicalName "More capability raises alignment risk through three channels" ;
