    :flowSummary "Rare reckless actions do not nullify Mythos's value, but they do produce an explicit recommendation not to deploy it in settings where harms would be hard to reverse." ;
    :flowTo :deployment_avoidance_for_hard_to_reverse_harms ;
    :flowVia :auto_mode_risk_reduction,
