    :entityCategory "finding" ;
    :findingText "The welfare introduction says Anthropic sees a growing possibility that advanced models may have experiences, interests, or welfare that matter intrinsically, while remaining deeply uncertain." ;
    :supportedBy :welfare_moral_uncertainty_quote .

