8.3 Agentic safety appendix                                                                              228
    8.3.1 Malicious use of agents                                                                        228
        8.3.1.1 Malicious use of Claude Code                                                             228
        8.3.1.2 Malicious computer use                                                                   229
        8.3.1.3 Malicious agentic influence campaigns                                                     230
    8.3.2 Prompt injection risk within agentic systems                                                    231
        8.3.2.1 External Agent Red Teaming benchmark for tool use                                         231
        8.3.2.2 Robustness against adaptive attackers across surfaces                                    232
             8.3.2.2.1 Coding                                                                            232
             8.3.2.2.2 Computer use                                                                      233
             8.3.2.2.3 Browser use                                                                       234
8.4 Per-question automated welfare interview results                                                     235
8.5 Blocklist used for Humanity's Last Exam                                                               242
8.6 SWE-bench Multimodal Test Harness                                                                    244

