    :pageText """Model                                         Attack success rate                   Attack success rate
                                              without safeguards                    with safeguards

                                              1 attempt          200                1 attempt          200
                                                                 attempts                              attempts

Claude           Extended thinking            0.0%               0.0%               0.0%               0.0%
Mythos
